            </span>
          </a>
          <div class="project-body">
            <p class="project-sector"><span class="pf-tag" data-tag="web-design">Web Design</span></p>
            <p>Contractor site with project gallery, financing modal, and bilingual EN/ES estimate request flow.</p>
          </div>
        </article>

        <article class="project-card pf-item" data-category="web-app">
          <a href="#" class="project-cover ph-6" aria-label="Atlas Logistics — Operations Portal">
            <span class="project-name">Atlas Logistics</span>
            <span class="pf-hover">
              <span class="btn is-secondary is-sm">Preview Website</span>
            </span>
          </a>
          <div class="project-body">
            <p class="project-sector"><span class="pf-tag" data-tag="web-app">Web App</span></p>
            <p>Operations portal with driver dispatch, document scanning, and live load-tracking dashboards.</p>
          </div>
